descriptionHtml:
[center][color=lightgreen][size=3]Description[/size][/color][/center][center]----------------[/center]
[center]
A set of fine dresses based on the barkeeper outfit.
The dresses can be bought at Radiant Raiment in solitude,or in a chest in QAsmoke.
you can also spawn the \"maid outfit chest\" with the command player.placeatme xxx 1
[/center]

[center][color=lightgreen][size=3]FAQ[/size][/color][/center][center]----------------[/center]


Q-
Where\'s she?I can\'t find her!

A-
She\'s in Jorrvasks
She\'s using companion\'s sandbox,and she\'ll move like the other companion.Make sure t chek bedrooms and outside ;)

And if you still can\'t find her,make sure the esp is active in your game launcher.MANUAL INSTALLATION IS RECOMMENDED.

Q-How can i remove her clothes?

A-you can do it in the ck
or with console commands:
Help \"name of the item you wish to remove\"
showinventory
removeitem xxxx 1
